/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, giving a sense of being in the midst of the action. The sky above is a clear blue, providing a vibrant backdrop to the urban landscape below. Buildings of various sizes and designs line the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. Power lines crisscross above, connecting the buildings and adding a touch of modernity to the scene. Trees dot the landscape, their green foliage contrasting with the concrete structures. People can be seen walking on the sidewalks, going about their day, adding a human element to the cityscape. The image is taken from a low angle, looking up at the buildings and power lines, giving a sense of scale and grandeur to the scene.
